{"tid":1391750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（8月5號）大家千祈唔好堵塞新清水灣道呀！！！","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:14:25.000Z","uid":19788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20f08fb1b3f7d7cf6772009fb13f03f024d5eb7d","tid":1391750,"uid":19788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"利申 借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新清水灣道（New Clear Water Bay Road）位於彩雲及四<br />\n順，兩端均連接清水灣道，屬東、西走向，亦是觀塘區及黃大仙區界線的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOKHg9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOKHg9p.png&h=172ceb2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果呢條路癱瘓咗，有好多住喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>紀律部隊宿舍</strong></span>嘅人會返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋住西貢嘅人都會出唔到黎 更加唔好講會影響到住喺嗰頭嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大量愛國人士</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n再一次懇求大家 唔好搞新清水灣道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a59f4986b91dd2cbfaa9f789ebe312832204d51","tid":1391750,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"c27e5ed858a77f1d1bcee68ce24dddae733aca2e","tid":1391750,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"推爆"}]}